    "lyricsHtml": "\n[Intro] <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Cm\">Cm</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Db2\">Db2</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Cm\">Cm</span>\n\n\n\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">(Cordas)</span>\n   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Cm\">Cm</span>                   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Db2\">Db2</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Cm\">Cm</span>\n\n\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">(Flauta)</span>\n  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Cm\">Cm</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Db2\">Db2</span>                     <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Cm\">Cm</span>\n\n\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">(Violão)</span>\n  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Cm\">Cm</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Db2\">Db2</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Cm\">Cm</span>\n\n\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">[Primeira Parte]</span>\n\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Cm\">Cm</span>                           <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Fm\">Fm</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">   Nosso amor que eu não esqueço</span>\n                    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G7\">G7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">E que teve o seu começo</span>\n                   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Cm\">Cm</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Numa festa de São João</span>\n\n( <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Db7\">Db7</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Fm\">Fm</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Db7\">Db7</span> )\n\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">[Segunda Parte]</span>\n\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Cm\">Cm</span>                    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Bb\">Bb</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">   Morre hoje sem foguete</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Bb7\">Bb7</span>                       <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Ab\">Ab</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">    Sem retrato e sem bilhete</span>\n      <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Ab7\">Ab7</span>         <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G7\">G7</span>  \n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Sem luar, sem violão</span>\n\n( <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Db7(9)\">Db7(9)</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G7\">G7</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Db7(9)\">Db7(9)</span> )\n\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">[Terceira Parte]</span>\n\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C7\">C7</span>                   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Fm\">Fm</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">   Perto de você me calo</span>\n      <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Dº\">Dº</span>           <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G7\">G7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Tudo penso e nada falo</span>\n                  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C7\">C7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Tenho medo de chorar</span>\n\n( <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Db7\">Db7</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C7\">C7</span> )\n\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">[Quarta Parte]</span>\n\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Fm\">Fm</span>                         <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Cm\">Cm</span> \n<span class=\"lyric-line\">   Nunca mais quero o seu beijo</span>\n                  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Db7\">Db7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Mas meu último desejo</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G7\">G7</span>                  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C\">C</span> \n<span class=\"lyric-line\">   Você não pode negar</span>\n\n( <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A7\">A7</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D7\">D7</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G7\">G7</span> )\n\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">[Quinta Parte]</span>\n\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C\">C</span>               <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A7\">A7</span>   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D7\">D7</span> \n<span class=\"lyric-line\">  Se alguma pessoa amiga</span>\n   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G7\">G7</span>               <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Dm\">Dm</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Pedir que você lhe diga</span>\n    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G7\">G7</span>              <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C\">C</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Se você me quer ou não</span>\n\n( <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Dbº\">Dbº</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Cº\">Cº</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Bº\">Bº</span> )\n\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">[Sexta Parte]</span>\n\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Cm\">Cm</span>                    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Bb\">Bb</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">   Diga que você me adora</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Bb7\">Bb7</span>                      <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Ab\">Ab</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">    Que você lamenta e chora</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Ab7\">Ab7</span>                <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G\">G</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">    A nossa separação</span>\n\n( <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A7\">A7</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D7\">D7</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G7\">G7</span> )\n\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">[Sétima Parte]</span>\n\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C\">C</span>                <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C#º\">C#º</span>   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D7\">D7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">  Às pessoas que eu detesto</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G7\">G7</span>                          <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Dm7(5-)\">Dm7(5-)</span> \n<span class=\"lyric-line\">   Diga sempre que eu não presto</span>\n         <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G7\">G7</span>           <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C\">C</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C7M\">C7M</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C7\">C7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Que meu lar é o botequim</span>\n    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F\">F</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Fm7\">Fm7</span>               <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C\">C</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Que eu     arruinei sua vida</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am\">Am</span>                        <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D7\">D7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">   Que eu não mereço a comida</span>\n       <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G7\">G7</span>           <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Cm\">Cm</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Que você pagou pra mim</span>\n\n[Interlúdio] <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Fm\">Fm</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G7\">G7</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C7\">C7</span>\n             <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Db7\">Db7</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C7\">C7</span>  \n\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">[Quarta Parte]</span>\n\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Fm\">Fm</span>                         <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Cm\">Cm</span> \n<span class=\"lyric-line\">   Nunca mais quero o seu beijo</span>\n                  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Db7\">Db7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Mas meu último desejo</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G7\">G7</span>                  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C\">C</span> \n<span class=\"lyric-line\">   Você não pode negar</span>\n\n[Final] <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Db7\">Db7</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C\">C</span>\n",
